Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.71,0:21:09.87,ED CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}在耳边细语的天使堕入凡间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.21,0:21:16.97,ED CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}我会将你温柔地蚕食殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:22.17,ED CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}It's my guilty
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.84,0:21:35.52,ED CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}回过神 眼瞳空洞地睁开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:38.00,ED CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}这暗蓝色的混凝土
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.00,0:21:40.48,ED CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}冰冷地将我包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.48,0:21:42.94,ED CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}Call my name and give me a kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.94,0:21:45.46,ED CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}而后将我揽入胸怀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.46,0:21:52.00,ED CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}用你那已经失去灵魂的躯体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.28,0:21:54.80,ED CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}濒临崩溃的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.80,0:22:02.15,ED CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}仍勉强维持姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.15,0:22:04.77,ED CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}我能看见那赤红绚丽的永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.77,0:22:08.85,ED CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}它就在我身旁放声歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.00,0:22:11.97,ED CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}What was I born for
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.97,0:22:15.77,ED CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}请深爱着我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.57,0:22:20.37,ED CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}我绝不离开你
